  "about": {
    "details": "<p>Incorporated in 2017, Ahmedabad based S. M. Gold Limited is a company engaged in the business of manufacturing and wholesale trading of mangalsutra jewelry. Mangalsutra contributes 90% of the earnings of the company.</p><p>A minor part of the company's business also includes other jewelry items like Rings, Chain, Nose-rings/Nose Pins, Earrings, Ear Chain, waist belts, Pendant Set/Pendant, Anklet, Zuda, Toe Ring, Bracelet, Bangles, wedding, and festive Jewellery.</p><p>The company sells jewelry items under the brand name of \"S. M. Gold - the House of Mangalsutra\".</p><p>The company's manufacturing unit is located at Ahmedabad.</p><p>It currently employs 9 employees on its payroll.</p>"
  },
